  <brief_title>A Safety Study of TTP4000 in Subjects With Alzheimer's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Phase 1 Study of 2 Escalating, Single Subcutaneous Doses to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Immunogenicity, and Pharmacokinetics of TTP4000 in Subjects With Alzheimer's Disease With Mild Cognitive Impairment</official_title>
