  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to examine the safety, tolerability, immunogenicity and
      pharmacokinetics of TTP4000 in subjects with Alzheimer's disease with mild cognitive
      impairment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
